        <h4 className="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">
          Gather Friend Perspectives
        </h4>
        <p className="text-blue-800 text-sm mb-4">
          Share this special link with friends to gather their unique perspectives on how your values show up in their lives. They&apos;ll be invited to share stories and insights about the meaningful ways you&apos;ve impacted them. You can find them in your profile page if you're logged in, or on the link above.
